418
00:33:18,055 --> 00:33:21,391
YOU WILL MAKE MY JOB
A LOT EASIER.

419
00:33:24,696 --> 00:33:27,464
[Chinese]

420
00:33:27,532 --> 00:33:30,934
[Male Interpreter]
DID YOU HAVE THE KNIFE TESTED
FOR BLOOD ?

