423
00:33:39,210 --> 00:33:42,346
[Male Interpreter]
A STRONG SMELL OF ALCOHOL
WAS COMING FROM HIM.

424
00:33:42,413 --> 00:33:44,681
HE WAS UNSTEADY,
CONFUSED.

425
00:33:44,749 --> 00:33:47,149
HE SEEMED SURPRISED
BY IT ALL.

426
00:33:47,217 --> 00:33:50,185
[Chinese]

427
00:33:50,187 --> 00:33:52,555
[Female Interpreter]
DID YOU FIND ALCOHOL
IN THE ROOM ?

428
00:33:52,622 --> 00:33:57,059
[Male Interpreter]
TWO EMPTY BOTTLES OF CHAMPAGNE,
