429
00:33:57,126 --> 00:33:59,861
I HAVE NO FURTHER QUESTIONS
FOR THIS WITNESS.

430
00:34:00,197 --> 00:34:02,665
[Female Interpreter]
ADVOCATE SHEN YUELIN.

431
00:34:02,732 --> 00:34:04,900
[Chinese]

432
00:34:04,967 --> 00:34:07,436
[Female Interpreter]
WHAT TIME DID YOU RECEIVE
THE CALL ABOUT SCREAMS...

433
00:34:07,504 --> 00:34:11,206
COMING FROM THE ACCUSED'S ROOM ?
[Male Interpreter]
APPROXIMATELY 5:45.

434
00:34:11,208 --> 00:34:13,842
[Female Interpreter]
AND ENTERED
THE ACCUSED'S ROOM WHEN ?

435
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:15,844
[Male Interpreter]
6:04 A.M.

436
00:34:15,912 --> 00:34:20,015
[Female Interpreter]
CAPTAIN, HOW WOULD YOU DESCRIBE
THE ACCUSED'S STATE OF MIND ?

437
00:34:20,083 --> 00:34:22,418
[Male Interpreter]
SURPRISED.

438
00:34:22,485 --> 00:34:26,522
[Female Interpreter]
IN THE SITUATION, WOULD YOU
DESCRIBE "SURPRISED"...

439
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:29,658
AS A RATIONAL RESPONSE ?
[Male Interpreter]
NO.

440
00:34:29,726 --> 00:34:33,562
[Female Interpreter]
WOULD YOU DESCRIBE "SURPRISED"
AS A SANE RESPONSE ?

441
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:35,764
WHAT WAS HE WAITING FOR,
HIS OWN ARREST ?

442
00:34:35,832 --> 00:34:38,534
OBJECTION !

443
00:34:38,601 --> 00:34:40,969
I'D LIKE TO CONFER
WITH MY ADVOCATE, YOUR HONOR.

444
00:34:45,275 --> 00:34:47,209
I AM NOT INSANE.

445
00:34:47,276 --> 00:34:50,078
I WAS NOT DRUNK.
I AM NOT GOING TO PLEAD
DIMINISHED CAPACITY.

446
00:34:50,146 --> 00:34:52,981
I AM OBLIGED TO DO
WHAT IS REQUIRED...

447
00:34:53,049 --> 00:34:54,983
TO AVOID
YOUR EXECUTION.

448
00:34:55,051 --> 00:34:58,554
[Female Interpreter]
ADVOCATE, DOES THE DEFENSE
HAVE FURTHER QUESTIONS...

449
00:34:58,622 --> 00:35:00,789
FOR THIS WITNESS ?
YES, I HAVE QUESTIONS.

450
00:35:00,857 --> 00:35:05,561
I AM NOT FINISHED.
ACCORDING TO ARTICLE 26
OF THE PROCEDURE LAW...

451
00:35:05,629 --> 00:35:09,164
OR ARTICLE 32 OF
THE AMENDED VERSION OF THE SAME,

452
00:35:09,232 --> 00:35:12,033
I HAVE THE RIGHT
TO DEFEND MYSELF...

453
00:35:12,101 --> 00:35:15,070
TO COMMENT ON AND ASK QUESTIONS
OF WITNESSES...

454
00:35:15,138 --> 00:35:17,439
EVEN IF MY ADVOCATE
HAS ALREADY QUESTIONED THEM.

455
00:35:17,507 --> 00:35:21,443
ACCUSED MOORE, THIS RIGHT
IS RARELY EXERCISED.

456
00:35:21,511 --> 00:35:24,913
I KNOW, BUT I DO HAVE
THE RIGHT TO EXERCISE IT,
YOUR HONOR.

457
00:35:24,981 --> 00:35:29,117
THE APPROPRIATE FORM OF ADDRESS
IS PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

458
00:35:29,185 --> 00:35:31,086
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

459
00:35:33,523 --> 00:35:35,491
YOU MAY PROCEED.

460
00:35:36,660 --> 00:35:38,594
ASK YOUR QUESTION.

461
00:35:38,662 --> 00:35:41,430
THANK YOU,
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

462
00:35:43,533 --> 00:35:45,467
CAPTAIN,

463
00:35:45,535 --> 00:35:50,739
YOU TESTIFIED THAT
YOU ENTERED MY ROOM AT 6:04.

464
00:35:50,807 --> 00:35:55,177
WHEN YOU ENTERED MY ROOM,
THE BLOOD YOU FOUND ON MY HANDS
AND SHIRT,

465
00:35:55,244 --> 00:35:57,646
WAS IT WET OR DRY ?

466
00:35:57,714 --> 00:35:59,848
[Male Interpreter]
DRY.

467
00:35:59,916 --> 00:36:04,386
DRY.  THE SCREAMS
WERE HEARD AT 5:45.

468
00:36:04,454 --> 00:36:07,856
WOULDN'T IT HAVE TAKEN
MORE THAT 19 MINUTES
FOR SO MUCH BLOOD TO DRY ?

469
00:36:09,025 --> 00:36:10,959
[Male Interpreter]
USUALLY, YES.

470
00:36:11,027 --> 00:36:14,763
SO THE MURDER MUST'VE
TAKEN PLACE BEFORE 5:45 A.M.

471
00:36:14,831 --> 00:36:16,565
[Male Interpreter]
PERHAPS.

472
00:36:16,633 --> 00:36:19,401
[Jack]
IF THE MURDER TOOK PLACE
BEFORE 5:45,

473
00:36:19,469 --> 00:36:22,204
WHO WAS THERE TO SCREAM
AT 5:45 ?

474
00:36:22,271 --> 00:36:24,906
[Male Interpreter]
PERHAPS YOU.

475
00:36:24,974 --> 00:36:27,743
PERHAPS ME ?  WHY WOULD I
HAVE BEEN SCREAMING ?

476
00:36:27,811 --> 00:36:31,112
YOU WERE DRUNK.
[Male Interpreter]
TWO BOTTLES OF SCOTCH...

477
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:35,116
HAD BEEN EMPTIED.
NO, NOT TWO BOTTLES.
ONLY ONE.  ONE BOTTLE.

478
00:36:35,184 --> 00:36:38,119
<i>I ORDERED ONE BOTTLE.
YOU CAN VERIFY THAT
FROM ROOM SERVICE RECORDS.</i>

479
00:36:38,187 --> 00:36:40,356
MR. MOORE.

480
00:36:42,859 --> 00:36:46,194
[Male Interpreter]
YOUR FINGERPRINTS WERE FOUND
ON BOTH BOTTLES.

481
00:36:46,262 --> 00:36:50,298
AND THE HOTEL RECORDS SHOW
THAT TWO BOTTLES WERE ORDERED.

482
00:36:50,367 --> 00:36:53,201
<i>[Chairman Xu]
ACCUSED MOORE,
ARE YOU FINISHED ?</i>

483
00:37:03,713 --> 00:37:07,549
<i>ACCUSED MOORE,
ARE YOU QUITE FINISHED ? </i>

484
00:37:07,884 --> 00:37:11,253
JUST ONE MORE QUESTION,
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

485
00:37:12,622 --> 00:37:15,624
CAPTAIN, DID YOU FIND
A GOLD LOCKET...

486
00:37:15,692 --> 00:37:18,226
<i>ON OR ABOUT THE PERSON
OF THE VICTIM, HONG LING ?</i>

487
00:37:18,395 --> 00:37:21,630
[Male Interpreter]
I HAVE NO INFORMATION
ABOUT A LOCKET.

488
00:37:21,698 --> 00:37:25,467
THERE WAS A LOCKET THERE.
I'M SURE THERE WAS.
WHERE IS IT NOW ?

489
00:37:25,535 --> 00:37:29,337
[Ma In Chinese]

490
00:37:29,405 --> 00:37:31,673
[Laughing]

491
00:37:32,842 --> 00:37:36,278
WHAT--  I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T GET A TRANSLATION.

492
00:37:36,345 --> 00:37:39,047
WHY ARE THEY LAUGHING ?

493
00:37:39,115 --> 00:37:41,417
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
HOW CAN I BE EXPECTED
TO MOUNT A DEFENSE...

494
00:37:41,484 --> 00:37:43,585
IF I CAN'T UNDERSTAND
THE PROCURATOR ?

495
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:47,389
THE PEOPLE'S ASSESSOR
MAY NOT BE INTERESTED
IN LISTENING, BUT I AM !

496
00:37:49,642 --> 00:37:51,894
<i>[Chairman Xu
  In Chinese]</i>

497
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:59,968
ACCUSED MOORE,
WHAT THE PROCURATOR SAID THAT
BROUGHT LEVITY TO THIS COURT...

498
00:38:00,036 --> 00:38:03,071
<i>WAS PERHAPS THE VICTIM
HAD A MAGIC WAND,</i>

499
00:38:03,139 --> 00:38:07,876
AND TURNED THE LOCKET
INTO A SECOND BOTTLE OF SCOTCH.

500
00:38:10,864 --> 00:38:14,616
ARE YOU FINISHED NOW,
ACCUSED MOORE ?

501
00:38:22,926 --> 00:38:25,427
YES, I AM FINISHED.

502
00:38:25,494 --> 00:38:27,729
[Female Interpreter]
THE COURT IS DISMISSED.

503
00:38:33,169 --> 00:38:36,405
IN OUR COUNTRY, IT IS WISE
NOT TO RAISE QUESTIONS...

504
00:38:36,472 --> 00:38:39,974
TO WHICH YOU DO NOT KNOW
THE ANSWER.
MY COUNTRY TOO.

505
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:45,647
IF YOU WISHED TO HAVE LAW BOOKS,
YOU SHOULD HAVE REQUESTED THEM
FROM ME.

506
00:39:42,605 --> 00:39:44,806
I HEAR YOU'VE
BEEN QUESTIONED.

507
00:39:44,874 --> 00:39:49,244
THEN YOU APPRECIATE
THE SITUATION I'M IN.
YOU SHOULD GO HOME.

508
00:39:49,312 --> 00:39:52,314
WHAT SHOULD I TELL DAVID
ABOUT HOFFMANN ?

509
00:39:52,382 --> 00:39:55,817
UH, TELL DAVID...
[Sighs]

510
00:39:55,885 --> 00:39:58,453
TO LET HOFFCO
HAVE THE SATELLITE.

511
00:39:58,521 --> 00:40:01,656
[Jack]
CONCENTRATE ON AMERICAN
CONTENT PRODUCTION.

512
00:40:01,724 --> 00:40:03,658
MAKE HOFFMANN PAY
THROUGH THE NOSE.

513
00:40:03,726 --> 00:40:06,895
YOU THINK THE WORLD'S WAITING
FOR PROGRAMMING FROM BONN ?

514
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:09,131
[Chuckles]
I DOUBT IT.

515
00:40:09,198 --> 00:40:12,467
[Ghery]
YEAH.  I MEAN,

516
00:40:12,535 --> 00:40:15,803
IF A CHINESE GUY WOKE UP
AT THE PLAZA HOTEL...

517
00:40:15,871 --> 00:40:18,640
<i>WITH A DEAD
AMERICAN GIRL...</i>

518
00:40:18,992 --> 00:40:22,010
IN HIS SUITE, AND
THE CHINESE GOVERNMENT TRIED
TO MUSCLE IN ON HIS TRIAL,

519
00:40:22,078 --> 00:40:24,179
<i>I KINDA SEE THEIR POINT.</i>

520
00:40:24,247 --> 00:40:26,748
YOUR LAWYER'S VERY GOOD.

521
00:40:26,815 --> 00:40:29,151
<i>SHE EVEN GOT A FEW
DISSIDENTS OFF.
GO ON.</i>

522
00:40:29,218 --> 00:40:31,953
[Jack]
GIVE MY BEST
TO JANIE AND THE KIDS.

523
00:40:32,021 --> 00:40:33,688
I WILL.

524
00:40:33,756 --> 00:40:36,624
<i>GET OUT OF HERE.
THANKS, JACK.</i>

525
00:40:36,692 --> 00:40:40,012
<i>I'LL BE BACK.</i>

526
00:40:42,331 --> 00:40:44,599
MR. MOORE ?

527
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:52,474
I HAVE SOME QUESTIONS...

528
00:40:52,542 --> 00:40:55,177
TO ASK YOU.

529
00:40:55,244 --> 00:40:57,245
BUT, UH...

530
00:40:58,948 --> 00:41:03,452
IF YOU STILL PREFER
THAT I RESIGN,
I WILL DO AS YOU WISH.

531
00:41:08,490 --> 00:41:11,158
NO, I DO NOT PREFER.

532
00:41:13,094 --> 00:41:15,162
[Bicycle Bell Rings]

533
00:41:16,164 --> 00:41:18,198
[Yuelin]
ROLL IT, PLEASE.

534
00:41:20,035 --> 00:41:23,137
<i>WHAT IS MY COUNTRY GIRL
WITH A CITY MOUTH
LOOKING FOR ?</i>

535
00:41:23,488 --> 00:41:26,072
THE TRUTH
ABOUT MY CLIENT.

536
00:41:29,810 --> 00:41:31,978
<i>WAIT.  FREEZE IT.</i>

537
00:41:34,882 --> 00:41:36,650
HIT "PLAY."

538
00:41:36,717 --> 00:41:39,085
I HAVE A CERTAIN SYMPATHY
FOR YOUR AMERICAN.

539
00:41:40,405 --> 00:41:43,139
ONE MAN
AGAINST EVERYONE.

540
00:41:43,207 --> 00:41:45,141
VERY COOL.

541
00:41:46,410 --> 00:41:48,411
PENG, BACK IT UP.

