[Chinese]

545
00:42:25,082 --> 00:42:28,251
WHAT ?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?

546
00:42:30,421 --> 00:42:32,689
NO, NO.

547
00:42:32,757 --> 00:42:36,626
NO !  YOU CANNOT HAVE
THIS BOOK !  NO !

548
00:42:36,694 --> 00:42:38,561
NO !  NO !
[Buzzing]

549
00:42:38,629 --> 00:42:41,197
NO, YOU CAN'T HAVE--
[Buzzing]

550
00:42:41,599 --> 00:42:44,768
NO !
[Groaning]

551
00:42:46,303 --> 00:42:49,439
<i>[Groaning Continues]</i>

552
00:44:09,086 --> 00:44:12,388
I WISH TO SPEAK
OF THE LOCKET YOU SAID
HONG LING WAS WEARING.

553
00:44:12,456 --> 00:44:15,825
SHE WAS WEARING A LOCKET.
I KNOW.  I HAVE CONFIRMATION
THAT SHE WAS.

554
00:44:15,893 --> 00:44:18,694
CONFIRMATION ?
YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE ME ?

555
00:44:20,131 --> 00:44:22,098
THE LOCKET WAS A GIFT
FROM HER FATHER.

556
00:44:22,166 --> 00:44:25,301
<i>HE ASKED
FOR ITS RETURN.
WHERE IS IT ?</i>

557
00:44:25,369 --> 00:44:27,871
IT HAS NOT BEEN FOUND.

558
00:44:29,440 --> 00:44:31,975
YOU FIND THAT INSIGNIFICANT ?

559
00:44:36,147 --> 00:44:38,098
<i>XIE XIE.</i>

560
00:44:40,684 --> 00:44:44,521
[Equipment Beeping]

561
00:44:48,026 --> 00:44:51,194
[Beeping]

562
00:44:56,834 --> 00:44:59,703
[Door Lock Clicks]

563
00:44:59,771 --> 00:45:02,305
OPEN THIS.

564
00:45:08,146 --> 00:45:11,114
I HAVE ALREADY
EXAMINED THIS.

565
00:45:13,350 --> 00:45:15,518
SMELL IT.

566
00:45:18,990 --> 00:45:22,059
WHAT DO YOU SMELL ?

567
00:45:22,126 --> 00:45:24,227
[Sniffs]

568
00:45:24,295 --> 00:45:27,030
- SOMETHING STRANGE.
- EXACTLY.

569
00:45:27,098 --> 00:45:31,634
[Female Interpreter]
DR. TAO, DO YOU DETECT
A CHEMICAL ODOR ON THIS SHIRT ?

570
00:45:31,702 --> 00:45:33,970
A FAMILIAR CHEMICAL ODOR ?

571
00:45:34,038 --> 00:45:36,139
[Male Interpreter]
THESE QUESTIONS
SERVE NO PURPOSE.

572
00:45:36,207 --> 00:45:39,676
- [Chairman Xu In Chinese]
- [Female Interpreter]
WE WILL SEE.  CONTINUE.

573
00:45:39,743 --> 00:45:44,247
[Female Interpreter]
GIVE US YOUR EXPERT OPINION TO
WHAT YOU BELIEVE THE ODOR TO BE.

574
00:45:44,315 --> 00:45:47,650
[Male Interpreter]
MAYBE CHLOROFORM
OR AN ETHER DERIVATIVE.

575
00:45:47,718 --> 00:45:52,589
[Female Interpreter]  COULD
CHLOROFORM OR ETHER BE USED
TO RENDER SOMEONE UNCONSCIOUS ?

576
00:45:52,656 --> 00:45:55,058
[Male Interpreter]
YES, IT COULD.  THESE QUESTIONS
WASTE THE COURT'S TIME.

577
00:45:55,126 --> 00:45:59,462
[Female Interpreter]
I WILL MAKE THAT DECISION.
CONTINUE.

578
00:45:59,530 --> 00:46:04,067
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
THE ACCUSED HAD NEITHER
CHLOROFORM NOR ETHER...

579
00:46:04,135 --> 00:46:07,403
IN HIS POSSESSION
AT THE TIME
HE ENTERED THE COUNTRY.

580
00:46:07,471 --> 00:46:12,342
AND NO AUTHORIZATION
WAS ISSUED FOR HIM
TO PURCHASE EITHER CHEMICAL.

581
00:46:12,409 --> 00:46:14,344
NEITHER CHEMICAL
WAS FOUND...

582
00:46:14,411 --> 00:46:16,546
<i>IN HIS HOTEL ROOM.</i>

583
00:46:16,614 --> 00:46:21,952
THEREFORE, THESE CHEMICALS
MUST'VE BEEN BROUGHT TO
THE CRIME SCENE BY SOMEONE ELSE.

584
00:46:22,019 --> 00:46:25,922
BY THE SOMEONE ELSE WHO RENDERED
MR. MOORE UNCONSCIOUS.

585
00:46:25,990 --> 00:46:28,892
BY THE SOMEONE ELSE
WHO MURDERED HONG LING.

586
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:31,427
<i>PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,</i>

587
00:46:31,495 --> 00:46:35,498
THE ACCUSED WISHES
TO CHANGE HIS PLEA
TO "NOT GUILTY."

588
00:46:38,870 --> 00:46:42,873
- [Chairman Xu In Chinese]
