GATHERED AT THE SCENE.

605
00:49:12,856 --> 00:49:15,558
WHY DO YOU PUT YOURSELF
AT RISK FOR THIS FOREIGNER ?

606
00:49:15,626 --> 00:49:19,062
- THIS FOREIGNER
