607
00:49:19,430 --> 00:49:21,998
<i>I MAY NOT BE ABLE
TO PROTECT YOU THIS TIME.</i>

608
00:49:22,066 --> 00:49:25,168
THANK YOU FOR YOUR CONCERN,
DIVISION CHIEF LI.

609
00:49:36,047 --> 00:49:39,082
<i>[Shouts In Chinese]</i>

610
00:49:50,093 --> 00:49:54,430
[People Chattering,
Baby Crying]

611
00:49:57,767 --> 00:49:59,768
[Knocks At Door]

612
00:50:06,443 --> 00:50:08,444
GOOD MORNING,
MR. MOORE.

613
00:50:10,213 --> 00:50:13,215
I WAS INFORMED
THAT YOU WERE ATTACKED
LAST NIGHT.

614
00:50:14,251 --> 00:50:16,185
ARE YOU OKAY ?
YEAH,
I'M ALL RIGHT.

615
00:50:16,253 --> 00:50:19,021
WHAT AM I DOING HERE ?
IT IS A PROVISIONAL
GUARANTEE.

616
00:50:19,088 --> 00:50:22,625
THE COURT WILL
NOT MEET TODAY SO THAT WE
MAY PREPARE YOUR DEFENSE.

617
00:50:22,692 --> 00:50:25,594
RIGHT.
EMBASSY FINALLY
GOT OFF ITS ASS.

618
00:50:25,662 --> 00:50:28,464
YOU MUST RETURN
TO CONFINEMENT...

619
00:50:28,532 --> 00:50:31,367
AT NIGHTFALL.

620
00:50:31,434 --> 00:50:34,470
WOULD YOU LIKE TEA,
MR. MOORE ?

621
00:50:35,605 --> 00:50:37,773
YES, TEA...
PLEASE.
OKAY.

622
00:50:44,147 --> 00:50:46,582
[Sighs]

