00:51:29,992 --> 00:51:32,294
THE WHAT ?
PIBA.

631
00:51:37,334 --> 00:51:39,335
[Clears Throat]

632
00:51:40,303 --> 00:51:43,439
WHAT DOES IT
SOUND LIKE ?

633
00:51:43,506 --> 00:51:47,142
WE HAVE MUCH TO DO.
NO, PLEASE.

634
00:51:47,210 --> 00:51:49,511
PLAY FOR ME.

635
00:51:54,884 --> 00:51:58,554
[Sighs]
I'D LIKE TO HEAR
SOME MUSIC AGAIN.

636
00:52:04,894 --> 00:52:06,895
[Strums Piba]

637
00:52:15,071 --> 00:52:23,545


638
00:52:37,427 --> 00:52:39,895
YOU HAVE BEAUTIFUL HANDS.

639
00:52:42,599 --> 00:52:44,533
WHY DID YOU STOP ?

640
00:52:45,835 --> 00:52:48,604
WE HAVE LITTLE TIME
AND MUCH TO DO.

641
00:52:52,575 --> 00:52:55,477
<i>[Chinese]</i>

642
00:52:55,545 --> 00:52:57,546
MY GRANDMOTHER.

643
00:53:01,418 --> 00:53:05,187
- [Chinese]
- [Chinese]

644
00:53:05,254 --> 00:53:07,423
- [Chinese]
- [Chinese]

645
00:53:07,490 --> 00:53:10,426
[Laughs]
IT'S A GREAT HONOR
TO MEET YOU.

646
00:53:14,464 --> 00:53:18,967
UH...
[Chinese]

647
00:53:19,035 --> 00:53:21,102
[Laughs,
Chinese]

648
00:53:21,170 --> 00:53:23,972
[Chinese]

649
00:53:26,776 --> 00:53:28,777
SO, YOUR PARENTS
ARE DECEASED ?

650
00:53:28,845 --> 00:53:31,213
YEAH.

651
00:53:31,280 --> 00:53:35,417
AND BROTHERS
AND SISTERS ?
NO.

652
00:53:35,485 --> 00:53:37,252
AND A WIFE ?

653
00:53:37,320 --> 00:53:39,921
NO WIFE.

654
00:53:39,989 --> 00:53:43,525
FOR US, TO BE WITHOUT A FAMILY
IS A TERRIBLE THING.

655
00:53:43,593 --> 00:53:47,062
BUT YOU'VE NEVER MARRIED.

656
00:53:47,129 --> 00:53:51,049
I HAVE BEEN UNABLE TO FIND A MAN
WHO'S NOT THREATENED
BY A WOMAN'S INTELLIGENCE.

657
00:53:51,117 --> 00:53:54,452
[Laughs]
WITH HALF A BILLION MEN IN THIS
COUNTRY, IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE.

658
00:53:54,520 --> 00:53:57,388
YES, ISN'T IT ?

659
00:53:57,456 --> 00:53:59,958
YOU HAD A PRESTIGIOUS...

660
00:54:00,026 --> 00:54:03,962
AND EXPENSIVE EDUCATION
AT HARVARD AND
STANFORD LAW SCHOOL.

661
00:54:04,030 --> 00:54:07,032
I HAD SCHOLARSHIPS.

662
00:54:07,099 --> 00:54:10,735
I SERVED DRINKS
AT RICH PEOPLE'S PARTIES.
YOU PURSUED LAW...

663
00:54:10,803 --> 00:54:14,172
BECAUSE YOU WANTED TO BE
ONE OF THE RICH PEOPLE
YOU SERVED ?

664
00:54:14,240 --> 00:54:16,274
NO.  I WANTED
TO BE IN CONTROL.

665
00:54:16,342 --> 00:54:18,376
AND WERE YOU ?

666
00:54:19,712 --> 00:54:21,646
I THOUGHT I WAS.

667
00:54:21,714 --> 00:54:23,414
UNTIL NOW.

668
00:54:23,482 --> 00:54:25,851
[Sighs]

669
00:54:33,459 --> 00:54:35,493
[Clears Throat]

670
00:54:36,829 --> 00:54:40,232
YOU ASKED ME IF I HAD A WIFE.
I SAID NO.

671
00:54:40,299 --> 00:54:42,968
I DON'T,
BUT I DID.

672
00:54:43,035 --> 00:54:46,471
WE HAD A DAUGHTER
SEVEN YEARS OLD.

673
00:54:46,538 --> 00:54:50,475
THEY WERE IN A TAXI
IN SAN FRANCISCO.
THERE WAS AN ACCIDENT.

674
00:54:52,711 --> 00:54:54,746
I AM SORRY.

675
00:54:56,115 --> 00:54:59,084
ANYTHING ELSE
YOU WANT TO KNOW ?

676
00:55:03,689 --> 00:55:08,526
UM...
WHAT WAS YOUR FIRST CONTACT
WITH HONG LING ?

677
00:55:08,594 --> 00:55:11,296
DO YOU THINK
I KILLED HER ?

678
00:55:11,397 --> 00:55:14,299
MY JOB IS TO FIND THE TRUTH,
TO HANDLE THIS CASE...

679
00:55:14,367 --> 00:55:16,534
ACCORDING TO LAW.

680
00:55:16,602 --> 00:55:20,005
DO YOU BELIEVE ME
OR NOT ?

681
00:55:20,072 --> 00:55:23,474
I HAVE GROWING QUESTIONS
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED THAT NIGHT.

682
00:55:25,378 --> 00:55:29,514
NOW, PLEASE TELL ME
OF YOUR FIRST CONTACT
WITH HONG LING.

683
00:55:41,160 --> 00:55:43,929
<i>[Yuelin]
DID YOU APPROACH HER ?</i>

684
00:55:43,996 --> 00:55:48,366
NO, SHE WAS--
SHE WAS MODELING.
SOME KIND OF FASHION SHOW.

685
00:55:48,434 --> 00:55:51,136
YOU SIMPLY SAW HER ?

686
00:55:51,203 --> 00:55:54,105
WE SAW EACH OTHER.
YOUR EYES MET ?

687
00:55:55,574 --> 00:55:57,575
I GUESS SO.
ARE YOU SURE ?

688
00:55:58,710 --> 00:56:00,645
YES, I'M SURE.

689
00:56:02,748 --> 00:56:05,350
SO YOU WERE
ATTRACTED TO HER ?

690
00:56:06,785 --> 00:56:09,654
YEAH.  YES,
I WAS ATTRACTED.

691
00:56:11,123 --> 00:56:14,025
BECAUSE SHE
WAS BEAUTIFUL ?

692
00:56:17,596 --> 00:56:20,365
[Sighs]
I GUESS SO.

693
00:56:36,615 --> 00:56:41,786
YOU APPROACHED HER LATER
WHEN YOU SAW HER AT THE TABLE ?

694
00:56:41,854 --> 00:56:44,422
I WAS OVER THERE.
SHE WAS OVER HERE.

695
00:56:44,490 --> 00:56:48,793
SHE WAS LOOKING AT ME
AND DRAWING SOMETHING.

696
00:56:48,861 --> 00:56:52,464
SO YOU WERE CURIOUS,
THEN YOU APPROACHED HER ?

697
00:56:52,531 --> 00:56:54,665
WHAT WAS SHE DRAWING ?

698
00:56:55,934 --> 00:56:59,837
<i>MY NOSE.
SHE SAID, "DA BI ZI."</i>

699
00:56:59,905 --> 00:57:02,540
[Laughs]

700
00:57:05,811 --> 00:57:10,248
<i>"DA BI ZI."
 IT MEANS... BIG NOSE.
BIG NOSE, YEAH.</i>

701
00:57:10,316 --> 00:57:12,484
THANKS.
[Laughs]

702
00:57:12,551 --> 00:57:15,186
WE WERE SITTING THERE
AND TALKING...

703
00:57:15,254 --> 00:57:18,623
AND LOOKING
AT HER DRAWINGS...

704
00:57:18,690 --> 00:57:20,691
AND LAUGHING.

705
00:57:23,695 --> 00:57:25,630
WE JUST CLICKED.

706
00:57:25,697 --> 00:57:27,298
"CLICKED."

707
00:57:27,366 --> 00:57:30,335
YOU MEAN CHEMISTRY.
IS THAT THE RIGHT WORD ?

708
00:57:30,403 --> 00:57:33,338
MM-HMM.
CHEMISTRY.  CLICKED.

709
00:57:34,806 --> 00:57:38,376
SO...
YOU ARE A ROMANTIC.

710
00:57:38,444 --> 00:57:42,647
<i>YOU WERE DRAWN
TO EACH OTHER.</i>

711
00:57:42,714 --> 00:57:44,649
DID YOU KISS ?

712
00:57:48,187 --> 00:57:50,188
NOT HERE, NO.

713
00:58:04,535 --> 00:58:07,303
TO RETURN HERE
IS DIFFICULT FOR YOU.

714
00:58:14,345 --> 00:58:19,149
DO YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING
UNUSUAL HAPPENING ?
THINK BACK.

715
00:58:19,217 --> 00:58:22,819
IS THAT THE PROPER WAY
TO SAY IT ?
THAT'S FINE.

716
00:58:29,693 --> 00:58:32,695
SHE GOT A PHONE CALL.
IT UPSET HER.

717
00:58:32,763 --> 00:58:36,266
- [Yuelin]
ON THE HOTEL PHONE ?
- NO, IT WAS ON HER CELLULAR.

718
00:58:36,333 --> 00:58:40,570
<i>SHE, UH--
SHE SAID IT WAS NOTHING.
PERIOD.  MEISHI.</i>

719
00:58:40,638 --> 00:58:42,939
<i>- MEISHI.
- MEISHI !  MEISHI !</i>

720
00:58:43,007 --> 00:58:45,008
[Chuckles]
ANYTHING ELSE ?

721
00:58:47,111 --> 00:58:49,579
SHE SAID--

722
00:58:49,647 --> 00:58:54,450
[Chinese]
DOES THAT MEAN ANYTHING ?

723
00:58:54,518 --> 00:58:58,054
NO.  YOU DID NOT
HEAR HER SCREAM ?

724
00:58:58,122 --> 00:58:59,689
NO, NO.

725
00:58:59,757 --> 00:59:02,225
BUT SOMEONE MADE
AN ANONYMOUS CALL
TO THE POLICE...

726
00:59:02,293 --> 00:59:05,595
<i>CLAIMING TO HEAR SCREAMS
COMING FROM THIS SUITE.</i>

727
00:59:08,332 --> 00:59:11,101
THIS IS AN OLD HOTEL,
ISN'T IT ?

728
00:59:11,169 --> 00:59:15,972
LET ME SEE.
IT'S VERY SOLIDLY CONSTRUCTED.

729
00:59:16,040 --> 00:59:19,342
OUTER DOOR
AND AN INNER DOOR.

730
00:59:24,682 --> 00:59:26,482
[Screams]

731
00:59:26,550 --> 00:59:30,553
<i>[Chinese]
NO, IT'S ALL RIGHT.
MEISHI, MEISHI.</i>

732
00:59:32,924 --> 00:59:35,625
YOU HEAR ANYTHING ?
NO.  COME.

733
00:59:40,731 --> 00:59:44,067
THESE ARE OBJECTS
HONG LING HAD WITH HER
IN THIS ROOM.

734
00:59:44,135 --> 00:59:46,970
THE POLICE DEVELOPED
THE PICTURES.

735
00:59:59,250 --> 01:00:04,187
THE LAST CALL SHE MADE
ON THIS PHONE WAS 5-1-7-8-5-7.

736
01:00:04,255 --> 01:00:06,622
IT HAS BEEN DISCONNECTED.

737
01:00:06,690 --> 01:00:10,493
- [Chinese]
- THERE MUST BE A CENTRAL
TELEPHONE EXCHANGE.

738
01:00:10,561 --> 01:00:14,097
THAT'S WHERE
THE BILLING RECORDS ARE KEPT.
WE ARE GOING THERE NOW.

739
01:00:14,165 --> 01:00:19,169
WHY ARE YOU SMILING ?
I'M USUALLY THE ONE WHO
FIGURES OUT THE NEXT STEP.

740
01:00:19,237 --> 01:00:20,837
OH.

741
01:00:20,904 --> 01:00:25,808
THIS MUST BE EXTREMELY DIFFICULT
TO RELY ON A STRANGER, A WOMAN,

742
01:00:25,876 --> 01:00:29,779
A FOREIGN WOMAN,
IN SUCH A SERIOUS MATTER.
THAT'S WHY I SMILED.

743
01:00:35,652 --> 01:00:37,954
YOU WILL WAIT HERE,
PLEASE.

744
01:00:38,022 --> 01:00:40,456
[Chinese]

745
01:00:44,762 --> 01:00:47,163
[Chinese]

746
01:00:49,100 --> 01:00:51,134
[Chinese]

747
01:00:54,438 --> 01:00:58,375
[TV Announcer
In Chinese]

748
01:00:59,293 --> 01:01:02,245
[Chinese]

749
01:01:13,924 --> 01:01:16,159
[Chinese]

750
01:01:16,227 --> 01:01:21,164
<i>[TV: Chinese]</i>

751
01:01:21,232 --> 01:01:23,866
[German]

752
01:01:23,935 --> 01:01:26,469
[Male Interpreter]
...HAS SELECTED
HOFFCO TELEKOMM...

753
01:01:26,537 --> 01:01:31,774
AS CHINA'S PARTNER
IN THIS MULTIBILLION DOLLAR
SATELLITE UNDERTAKING.

754
01:01:36,980 --> 01:01:38,848
[Chinese]

755
01:01:38,916 --> 01:01:42,652
[Chinese]

756
01:01:47,557 --> 01:01:49,826
[Chinese]

757
01:01:55,499 --> 01:01:57,767
[Jack]
WHAT'S WRONG ?

758
01:01:59,236 --> 01:02:03,273
THE RECORDS
CANNOT BE ACCESSED.
THEY HAVE BEEN DELETED.

759
01:02:03,341 --> 01:02:05,342
BY WHOM ?

760
01:02:06,910 --> 01:02:09,479
DO NOT TALK
ABOUT THIS HERE.

761
01:02:10,848 --> 01:02:13,516
WHO DELETED THE RECORDS ?

762
01:02:13,584 --> 01:02:17,887
WHO HAS THE POWER
TO DELETE TELEPHONE RECORDS ?
COULD YOU DELETE YOUR RECORDS ?

763
01:02:17,955 --> 01:02:20,457
YOU COULDN'T, COULD YOU ?
'CAUSE YOU'RE NOT
A GOVERNMENT OFFICIAL.

764
01:02:20,524 --> 01:02:24,427
ONLY A GOVERNMENT OFFICIAL
COULD AUTHORIZE THE DELETION
OF THESE RECORDS.

765
01:02:24,495 --> 01:02:29,099
IS THAT IT ?
IS THAT TRUE ?
WHOEVER LING CALLED THAT NIGHT--

766
01:02:29,166 --> 01:02:32,002
MIGHT KNOW SOMETHING ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED.  DO NOT SAY MORE.
WE MUST LEAVE NOW.

767
01:02:32,069 --> 01:02:35,571
IF THAT PERSON IS A GOVERNMENT
OFFICIAL OF A GOVERNMENT
I'M NEGOTIATING WITH--

768
01:02:35,639 --> 01:02:39,909
IF I COULD BE EMBARRASSED
OR DISCREDITED IN SOME WAY,

769
01:02:39,977 --> 01:02:42,412
MAYBE HE GETS A BETTER DEAL
WITH MY COMPETITOR.

770
01:02:42,480 --> 01:02:44,414
SWEET SYSTEM
YOU'VE GOT HERE.

771
01:02:44,482 --> 01:02:47,817
THE RECORDS WERE NOT DELETED
BY THE SYSTEM.  THEY WERE
DELETED BY AN INDIVIDUAL.

772
01:02:47,885 --> 01:02:49,986
INDIVIDUAL.  OKAY.
I'LL GO WITH THAT.

773
01:02:50,054 --> 01:02:54,491
WHO DO WE HAVE ?
WE HAVE MINISTER LIN SHOU
AND HERR HOFFMANN.

774
01:02:54,558 --> 01:02:56,859
NO.
WHAT ABOUT GENERAL HONG ?

775
01:02:56,927 --> 01:03:01,164
IT IS NOT GENERAL HONG.
WHY NOT ?  HE'S GOT INFLUENCE
WITH THE P.S.B., WITH EVERYBODY.

776
01:03:01,232 --> 01:03:04,700
GENERAL HONG IS NOT CORRUPT.
HE ONLY WANTS THE KILLER
OF HIS DAUGHTER PUNISHED.

777
01:03:04,768 --> 01:03:07,103
HE'S OLD GUARD !
HE'S LOSING CONTROL.

778
01:03:07,171 --> 01:03:09,139
YOU DO NOT UNDERSTAND.

779
01:03:09,206 --> 01:03:13,843
<i>NO, YOU DO NOT UNDERSTAND !
THIS IS A SATELLITE
COMMUNICATIONS DEAL.</i>

780
01:03:13,911 --> 01:03:17,047
AND FOR BETTER OR FOR WORSE,
THE EFFECT
OF THE McANDREWS DEAL...

781
01:03:17,114 --> 01:03:19,249
WOULD HAVE BEEN TO OPEN
A TOTALLY CLOSED SYSTEM.

782
01:03:19,316 --> 01:03:22,885
WHO ARE YOU TO CRITICIZE ?
ONCE THAT SYSTEM OPENS UP,
THERE'S NO GOING BACK.

783
01:03:22,953 --> 01:03:25,821
YOU COME FROM A COUNTRY
WHERE THE INFANT MORTALITY
RATE IS HIGHER THAN OURS.

784
01:03:25,889 --> 01:03:28,458
THE REASON YOU KNOW THAT
IS WE DON'T DELETE THE RECORDS.

785
01:03:28,526 --> 01:03:32,161
- WHERE PEOPLE ARE PUNISHED
FOR THE COLOR OF THEIR SKIN.
- HAVE YOU EVER BEEN THERE ?

786
01:03:32,229 --> 01:03:35,298
YOU FIND IT EASY TO ASSUME
THAT A CHINESE FATHER
WOULD KILL HIS DAUGHTER...

787
01:03:35,366 --> 01:03:37,300
TO STOP YOUR PRECIOUS
BUSINESS DEAL !

788
01:03:37,368 --> 01:03:40,503
I DO NOT FIND THAT EASY
TO ASSUME.

789
01:03:40,571 --> 01:03:42,972
HOW MANY PEOPLE
ARE KILLED EACH WEEK
IN YOUR PEACEFUL COUNTRY ?

790
01:03:43,040 --> 01:03:45,007
I DON'T FIND THAT EASY
TO ASSUME.

791
01:03:45,075 --> 01:03:48,478
HOW MANY, MR. MOORE ?

792
01:03:49,880 --> 01:03:52,882
TOO MANY.

793
01:04:18,942 --> 01:04:21,344
[Horn Honking]

794
01:04:24,114 --> 01:04:25,848
[Shouting]

795
01:04:29,152 --> 01:04:31,120
[Horns Honking]

796
01:04:39,963 --> 01:04:42,265
[Honking]

797
01:05:24,473 --> 01:05:26,874
[Gunshot]

798
01:05:30,429 --> 01:05:32,530
[Gunshots]

799
01:05:41,941 --> 01:05:44,342
[Groans]

800
01:05:45,895 --> 01:05:47,813
[Gunshot]

801
01:05:51,617 --> 01:05:54,252
JACK !

802
01:05:54,320 --> 01:05:56,387
<i>- [Jack]  I GOTTA GO !
 - JACK, DON'T !</i>

803
01:05:56,455 --> 01:05:58,790
<i>JACK !</i>

804
01:05:58,857 --> 01:06:00,859
<i>JACK !</i>

805
01:06:01,827 --> 01:06:04,129
[Shouting]

806
01:06:12,205 --> 01:06:14,672
[P.S.B. Officer]
STOP !

807
01:06:19,378 --> 01:06:21,779
[Woman Shouts]
SORRY !

808
01:06:23,615 --> 01:06:26,067
SORRY !

809
01:06:26,135 --> 01:06:29,487
[Shouting]

810
01:06:37,163 --> 01:06:39,164
GET OUTTA MY WAY !

811
01:06:45,872 --> 01:06:49,507
[Horns Honking]
[Shouts]

812
01:06:57,616 --> 01:06:59,617
LOOK OUT !

813
01:06:59,685 --> 01:07:03,188
[Shouting,
Excited Chatting]

814
01:07:18,537 --> 01:07:21,006
LOOK OUT !  LOOK OUT !

815
01:07:22,341 --> 01:07:23,775
[Chinese]

816
01:07:29,548 --> 01:07:31,216
SHIT !

817
01:07:34,220 --> 01:07:36,687
[Shouting]

818
01:07:41,060 --> 01:07:43,094
[Chinese]

819
01:07:50,136 --> 01:07:52,003
[Babbles]

820
01:07:52,071 --> 01:07:54,239
[Quacking]

821
01:08:06,952 --> 01:08:08,420
SHH.  SHH.

822
01:08:08,487 --> 01:08:10,588
<i>[Chinese]</i>

823
01:08:11,890 --> 01:08:14,092
[Shouting
In Chinese]

824
01:08:16,929 --> 01:08:20,331
[Motorcycle Engine
Revving]

825
01:08:28,440 --> 01:08:31,175
[Revving Continues]

826
01:08:35,180 --> 01:08:38,282
<i>[Officer Yelling
  In Chinese]</i>

827
01:08:55,000 --> 01:08:57,368
[Chinese]

828
01:09:02,942 --> 01:09:06,060
[Chinese]

829
01:09:36,959 --> 01:09:40,662
<i>- [Old Woman Shouting]
 - [P.S.B. Officers
     In Chinese]</i>

830
01:09:45,167 --> 01:09:46,701
[Gunfire]
[Chinese]

831
01:09:47,736 --> 01:09:49,804
[Chinese]

832
01:10:00,816 --> 01:10:03,918
<i>[Chinese]</i>

833
01:10:21,370 --> 01:10:23,905
[Chinese]

834
01:11:25,968 --> 01:11:27,635
[Camera Shutter Clicking]

835
01:11:30,656 --> 01:11:33,090
<i>[Girls Scream]</i>

836
01:11:41,984 --> 01:11:45,153
[Chinese]

837
01:11:50,893 --> 01:11:54,361
[Siren Wailing]

838
01:11:59,618 --> 01:12:02,269
[Wailing Continues]

839
01:12:04,573 --> 01:12:06,841
[Siren Wailing]

840
01:12:21,924 --> 01:12:26,026
OPEN UP !
I'M AN AMERICAN CITIZEN
SEEKING ASYLUM !

841
01:12:26,094 --> 01:12:28,429
- [Siren Wailing]
- OPEN UP !

842
01:12:28,496 --> 01:12:33,768
MAY I SEE YOUR PASSPORT, SIR ?
IF I HAD A PASSPORT,
I WOULDN'T NEED ASYLUM !

843
01:12:36,404 --> 01:12:40,574
PLEASE,
YOU'VE GOTTA LET ME IN.
LET ME MAKE A PHONE CALL.

844
01:12:40,642 --> 01:12:43,311
[Siren Wailing]

845
01:12:52,587 --> 01:12:56,123
OH, MAN.
PRATT,
I'M REQUESTING ASYLUM.

846
01:12:56,191 --> 01:12:59,327
THIS IS A CONFIDENTIAL MATTER.
THIS IS NOT THE PLACE FOR US
TO HOLD THIS DISCUSSION.

847
01:12:59,394 --> 01:13:01,362
WE GOTTA
HOLD IT SOMEWHERE.
VERY GOOD ACOUSTICS.

848
01:13:01,430 --> 01:13:05,399
THIS USED TO BE THE PAKISTANI
EMBASSY.  BEFORE THAT, IT WAS
WIRED TO THE HILT BY THE P.R.C.

849
01:13:05,467 --> 01:13:07,634
FOLLOW ME.

850
01:13:09,771 --> 01:13:13,607
[Pratt]
THIS, HOWEVER,
IS ENTIRELY BUG FREE.

851
01:13:16,811 --> 01:13:18,379
MR. MOORE.

852
01:13:18,447 --> 01:13:21,582
PEYTON REED.
JACK.

853
01:13:21,649 --> 01:13:25,419
THE AMBASSADOR HAS ALREADY
BEEN SUMMONED TO SEE THE
MINISTER OF EXTERNAL AFFAIRS.

854
01:13:25,487 --> 01:13:29,656
THIS HAS THE MAKINGS
OF A FULL-SCALE INCIDENT.

855
01:13:29,724 --> 01:13:32,059
FULL-SCALE INCIDENT !

856
01:13:32,127 --> 01:13:34,428
[Laughing]

857
01:13:34,496 --> 01:13:36,997
SORRY I DIDN'T CALL
FOR AN APPOINTMENT.

858
01:13:41,136 --> 01:13:46,640
DO THE TWO OF YOU
HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT I'VE BEEN THROUGH ?

859
01:13:46,708 --> 01:13:50,978
- NO.  I AM NOT LEAVING HERE.
- NO ONE SAID YOU SHOULD LEAVE.

860
01:13:51,045 --> 01:13:53,314
I'M NOT GOING.
[Pratt]
OF COURSE NOT.

861
01:13:53,382 --> 01:13:55,949
NO, YOU'RE IN... BUT
GETTING OUT IS ANOTHER STORY.

862
01:13:56,017 --> 01:13:58,585
YOU'VE GOTTEN OTHER PEOPLE OUT.
YOU CAN GET ME OUT.

863
01:13:58,653 --> 01:14:01,822
IT TOOK US A YEAR TO GET
THOSE CHINESE PHYSICISTS OUT,
FANG LIZHI AND HIS WIFE.

864
01:14:01,890 --> 01:14:05,926
AND THE CHINESE ARMY THREATENED
TO STORM THE EMBASSY.

865
01:14:05,994 --> 01:14:09,163
THAT WAS A SIMPLE ASYLUM CASE.
YOU'RE CHARGED
WITH A CAPITAL CRIME.

866
01:14:09,231 --> 01:14:13,033
THIS BECOMES AN INTERNATIONAL
DICK-MEASURING CONTEST,
THEY MIGHT NEVER LET YOU LEAVE.

867
01:14:20,975 --> 01:14:22,910
WHAT ?

868
01:14:22,977 --> 01:14:27,114
WHAT IS IT ?
YOUR ATTORNEY SHEN YUELIN
IS AT THE GUARD STATION.

869
01:14:27,182 --> 01:14:29,650
SHE WISHES TO SEE YOU.
I WOULD ADVISE
NO CONTACT.

870
01:14:29,717 --> 01:14:32,920
<i>[Pratt]  IT WILL ONLY
MAKE THINGS HARDER FOR HER.</i>

871
01:14:32,987 --> 01:14:35,189
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?
- YUELIN PUT UP YOUR GUARANTEE.

872
01:14:35,257 --> 01:14:37,891
<i>I THOUGHT THE EMBASSY
PUT IT UP.
NO.</i>

873
01:14:37,959 --> 01:14:40,994
IN CHINA, BAIL HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH MONEY.
IT'S REPUTATION.

874
01:14:41,062 --> 01:14:45,666
[Reed]  TO HAVE YOU
RELEASED TODAY SO THAT
SHE COULD PREPARE A DEFENSE,

875
01:14:45,733 --> 01:14:48,602
SHEN YUELIN PUT UP
HER CAREER, HER FUTURE.

876
01:14:48,670 --> 01:14:50,771
IT WAS REALLY
QUITE UNIQUE.

877
01:14:53,708 --> 01:14:56,994
[Sirens Wailing]

878
01:15:01,265 --> 01:15:03,266
YUELIN ?

879
01:15:05,236 --> 01:15:07,170
YOUR SHOULDER !

880
01:15:07,238 --> 01:15:09,573
OH, IT'S ALL RIGHT.

881
01:15:11,609 --> 01:15:15,946
- IF I'D KNOWN WHAT YOU DID
FOR ME, I WOULDN'T HAVE LEFT.
- I'M GLAD YOU LEFT.

882
01:15:16,014 --> 01:15:18,281
<i>GLAD ?
YES.</i>

883
01:15:18,349 --> 01:15:23,854
BECAUSE I'M NOT SURE
I COULD HAVE SAVED YOU FROM
THE DECISION OF THE COURT.

884
01:15:23,922 --> 01:15:28,091
AND I... I COULD NOT
HAVE LIVED WITH THAT.

885
01:15:31,329 --> 01:15:34,365
WHY DID YOU RISK
YOUR LIFE FOR ME
IF YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE ME ?

886
01:15:36,367 --> 01:15:38,702
I ALWAYS ASSUMED THE WORST
ABOUT YOU.

887
01:15:38,770 --> 01:15:41,538
<i>I HAVE NEVER QUESTIONED.</i>

888
01:15:41,605 --> 01:15:46,076
I HAVE ALWAYS
ACCEPTED THINGS.

889
01:15:46,144 --> 01:15:49,246
<i>IT IS THE SAME
AS WHEN I WAS A CHILD.
WHY ?</i>

890
01:15:49,313 --> 01:15:52,215
I WAS BLIND.

891
01:15:52,283 --> 01:15:55,719
<i>I WAS MUTE.
WHEN YOU WERE A CHILD,</i>

892
01:15:57,288 --> 01:16:01,491
IT WAS DURING
THE CULTURAL REVOLUTION,
WASN'T IT ?
YES.

893
01:16:06,130 --> 01:16:08,432
WHAT IS IT ?

894
01:16:08,499 --> 01:16:12,636
<i>I WENT TO SCHOOL
UNTIL THEY CLOSED DOWN
AND EVERYTHING WENT MAD.</i>

895
01:16:15,740 --> 01:16:19,209
I DO NOT KNOW IF YOU COULD
UNDERSTAND THIS, JACK MOORE.

896
01:16:19,277 --> 01:16:21,294
TRY ME.

897
01:16:24,098 --> 01:16:27,067
I... I WATCHED--

898
01:16:28,403 --> 01:16:33,741
I WATCHED MY FATHER
BE HUMILIATED,
AND I SAID NOTHING.

899
01:16:33,808 --> 01:16:38,779
I WATCHED MY FATHER
BE SPAT ON.
I DID NOTHING.

900
01:16:38,847 --> 01:16:44,018
I EVEN WATCHED
MY CLASSMATES POUR BLACK INK
OVER HIS HEAD...

901
01:16:44,085 --> 01:16:49,356
ONE AFTER ANOTHER
AND AFTER ANOTHER.

902
01:16:50,392 --> 01:16:52,426
WHAT DID I DO ?

903
01:16:53,928 --> 01:16:58,665
I HID MY HEAD IN SHAME
WHILE HE WAS DRAGGED AWAY.

904
01:17:04,139 --> 01:17:06,673
I NEVER QUESTIONED.

905
01:17:06,741 --> 01:17:09,543
<i>I WAS BLIND.</i>

906
01:17:11,329 --> 01:17:14,764
I'M VERY SORRY
THAT I DID NOT BELIEVE
YOUR INNOCENCE.

907
01:17:18,769 --> 01:17:21,271
BUT NOW, I DO.

908
01:17:23,040 --> 01:17:24,808
I DO.

909
01:17:51,903 --> 01:17:56,339
SOMEBODY ALERTED THE PRESS.
LET'S GET YOU OUT OF HERE...

910
01:17:56,407 --> 01:18:00,810
<i>BEFORE YOUR FACE IS ON THE COVER
OF TIME AND NEWSWEEK.</i>

911
01:18:06,150 --> 01:18:09,219
[Excited Chatting]

912
01:20:00,897 --> 01:20:04,000
[Whispering]
WO MEN.

913
01:20:04,067 --> 01:20:05,801
[Chinese]

914
01:20:07,771 --> 01:20:09,606
[Chinese]

915
01:20:11,942 --> 01:20:14,577
WO MEN GUANXI--

916
01:20:44,691 --> 01:20:47,493
[Phone Dialing]

917
01:20:48,895 --> 01:20:50,696
[Gasps]

918
01:21:16,322 --> 01:21:19,692
A CERTAIN GENERAL
HAS A PERSONAL INTEREST...

919
01:21:19,760 --> 01:21:23,195
IN SEEING THAT SOME
OF THIS EVIDENCE IS RETURNED.

920
01:21:23,263 --> 01:21:26,632
IF, BY CHANCE, ANY ONE
OF THE ARRESTING OFFICERS...

921
01:21:26,700 --> 01:21:30,036
POCKETED THIS EVIDENCE
AND IT IS NOT RETURNED,

922
01:21:30,103 --> 01:21:34,373
THEN EVEN AN ATTORNEY
AS GOOD AS I AM
CANNOT ENSURE YOUR WELL-BEING.

923
01:21:34,440 --> 01:21:37,376
I SUGGEST
THAT YOU SEARCH AGAIN.

924
01:21:37,443 --> 01:21:42,447
ANYTHING YOU MIGHT TURN UP CAN
BE GIVEN TO MY AIDE AND BROUGHT
TO THE COURT FOR SAFEKEEPING.

925
01:22:00,600 --> 01:22:03,368
[Rifle Shots]

926
01:22:12,979 --> 01:22:15,414
[Rifle Shots]

927
01:22:18,785 --> 01:22:21,486
<i>[Door Opens]</i>

928
01:22:22,689 --> 01:22:25,057
[Door Closes]

929
01:22:49,382 --> 01:22:53,052
I NEED YOUR COUNSEL.
I WANT YOU TO WALK AWAY
FROM THIS.

930
01:22:53,120 --> 01:22:57,322
I'M TRYING TO GET ACCESS
TO EVIDENCE WHICH WOULD HELP
TO PROVE YOUR INNOCENCE.

931
01:22:57,390 --> 01:23:01,127
NO.  I WANT YOU
TO WALK AWAY NOW.
WHY DID YOU NOT ?

932
01:23:01,194 --> 01:23:03,328
THE SMART THING
WOULD HAVE BEEN
TO STAY AT THE EMBASSY.

933
01:23:03,396 --> 01:23:07,733
YEAH.  AND MOVE PAST IT.
YES, I DO THAT REALLY WELL.

934
01:23:07,800 --> 01:23:11,203
WHY DID YOU NOT ?

935
01:23:16,076 --> 01:23:18,944
DID YOU EVER SEE LITTLE GIRLS
PLAY SOCCER ?

936
01:23:19,012 --> 01:23:22,748
LITTLE... SILLY BUNDLES
OF ENERGY...

937
01:23:22,816 --> 01:23:27,019
SWARMING ALL OVER EACH OTHER,
TRIPPING ON EACH OTHER.

938
01:23:27,087 --> 01:23:31,523
HAIR RIBBONS
LEFT ON THE GROUND
WHEN THEY'RE THROUGH.

939
01:23:31,591 --> 01:23:33,442
YOUR DAUGHTER ?

940
01:23:33,510 --> 01:23:36,495
YEAH.  THEY WERE--

941
01:23:43,570 --> 01:23:47,773
THEY WERE DRIVING BACK
FROM A GAME WHEN IT HAPPENED,
THE ACCIDENT.

942
01:23:47,841 --> 01:23:50,276
AND YOU WERE ?

943
01:23:50,310 --> 01:23:53,012
I WAS IN TOKYO.
I WAS--

944
01:23:55,715 --> 01:23:57,950
I WAS CLOSING A DEAL.

945
01:23:58,018 --> 01:24:00,920
I COULD HAVE FINISHED IT
THE DAY BEFORE
IF I'D WANTED TO.

946
01:24:02,289 --> 01:24:06,192
YOU CANNOT BLAME YOURSELF.
NO, I DIDN'T.
I SET IT ASIDE.

947
01:24:06,260 --> 01:24:10,696
I JUST MOVED PAST IT.
BUILT A WALL AROUND IT.

948
01:24:11,999 --> 01:24:15,567
I HIRED SOMEBODY TO CLOSE UP
THE HOUSE IN SAN FRANCISCO.

949
01:24:15,635 --> 01:24:18,037
I GOT ON A PLANE,

950
01:24:18,105 --> 01:24:21,440
WENT SOMEWHERE
TO DO SOMETHING.

951
01:24:22,810 --> 01:24:25,945
AND I DID IT AGAIN
AND AGAIN,

952
01:24:26,013 --> 01:24:28,447
AND I ENDED UP HERE.

953
01:24:30,417 --> 01:24:33,552
BUT WHAT YOU LEAVE BEHIND
CATCHES UP WITH YOU.

954
01:24:35,255 --> 01:24:38,624
TOOK ME A LONG TIME
TO LEARN THAT.

955
01:24:40,060 --> 01:24:43,395
IF I HAD STAYED IN THE EMBASSY,
YOU WOULD HAVE BEEN IN DANGER.

956
01:24:43,463 --> 01:24:47,099
I AM NOT MOVING PAST THIS.

957
01:24:51,404 --> 01:24:53,406
JACK.

958
01:24:55,275 --> 01:24:58,577
YOU ONCE OFFERED TO RESIGN.

959
01:25:00,080 --> 01:25:03,282
I WANT YOU TO DO THAT.
I WANT YOU TO DO THAT NOW.

960
01:25:08,455 --> 01:25:11,157
MY DUTY IS TO PROVE
YOUR INNOCENCE.

961
01:25:11,225 --> 01:25:13,726
IT IS ALSO--

962
01:25:13,793 --> 01:25:16,896
IT IS ALSO MY WISH.

963
01:25:17,797 --> 01:25:21,300
<i>COURAGE.  YONG QI.</i>

964
01:26:28,367 --> 01:26:30,368
[Door Opens]

965
01:26:32,371 --> 01:26:35,306
[Door Closes]

966
01:26:43,582 --> 01:26:45,583
[Sighs]

967
01:27:41,574 --> 01:27:43,742
<i>YUELIN ?</i>

968
01:27:56,789 --> 01:27:59,024
WHY DID YOU COME HERE ?

969
01:27:59,092 --> 01:28:01,559
I AM HERO !

970
01:28:01,627 --> 01:28:05,731
A RECORD OF CALLS MADE TO
AND FROM HER CELL PHONE...

971
01:28:05,798 --> 01:28:08,066
AND A PRINTOUT AT HOME.

972
01:28:08,134 --> 01:28:11,169
PENG !
WHERE DID YOU GET THIS ?

973
01:28:11,237 --> 01:28:15,073
MY FRIEND MAI.
SHE SAY I AM
THE WORLD'S GREATEST LOVER.

974
01:28:15,141 --> 01:28:17,909
AND NOW I AM HERO TOO.

975
01:28:20,479 --> 01:28:24,950
PENG, HOW DID YOU
TALK YOUR WAY PAST
THE SECURITY MAN OUTSIDE ?

976
01:28:25,017 --> 01:28:28,086
I DID NOT HAVE TO.
THERE WAS NOBODY THERE.

977
01:28:30,757 --> 01:28:34,325
COME, PENG,
YOU LEAVE NOW.
GO ON, LEAVE.

978
01:28:40,233 --> 01:28:41,833
[Gasps]

979
01:28:46,172 --> 01:28:48,657
[Groaning]

980
01:28:48,724 --> 01:28:50,892
- [Screams]
- YUELIN ?

981
01:28:58,751 --> 01:29:01,419
[Gasping]

982
01:29:01,487 --> 01:29:03,621
[Coughing]

983
01:29:11,264 --> 01:29:16,234
[Pratt]  IT DOESN'T BRIGHTEN
THE SITUATION THAT YOUR ATTORNEY
GOT ROUGHED UP LAST NIGHT.

984
01:29:16,302 --> 01:29:20,238
MY ATTORNEY GOT WHAT ?
SHE WAS A TRACE ROUGHED UP
LAST NIGHT.

985
01:29:20,306 --> 01:29:24,075
A LITTLE BRUISED
IS ALL.
BRUISED ?  WHAT--
BY WHO ?

986
01:29:24,143 --> 01:29:26,211
SHE DIDN'T KNOW WHO.

987
01:29:26,279 --> 01:29:30,782
SHE WAS IN THE HOTEL SUITE WHERE
THE VICTIM EXPIRED.  SHE'S MORE
SHOOK UP THAN ANYTHING.

988
01:29:30,849 --> 01:29:33,451
STOP.  GO BACK.
NO, I'M AFRAID
THERE'S NO STOPPING IT NOW.

989
01:29:33,519 --> 01:29:37,189
THE INSTANT YOU LEFT SANCTUARY,
YOU WAY OVERSHOT ANY POINT
OF POSSIBLE RETURN.

990
01:29:37,256 --> 01:29:40,959
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE SAYING !
YOU LEFT
THE EMBASSY OUT ON A LIMB.

991
01:29:41,027 --> 01:29:45,730
- WE'VE GOT ZERO OPTIONS.
- THE EMBASSY OUT ON A LIMB ?
WHAT ABOUT HER ?

992
01:29:45,798 --> 01:29:51,569
<i>-YOU DIDN'T MAKE OUR JOB EASIER.
-ALL RIGHT !  MEISHI !
 WHAT ABOUT HER ?</i>

993
01:29:51,637 --> 01:29:56,741
- I TOLD YOU NOT TO TALK TO HER.
- HOW ?  SHE'S THE ONE PUTTING
HERSELF ON THE LINE FOR ME !

994
01:29:56,809 --> 01:29:59,044
SHE'S NOT OUR JOB.

995
01:30:03,349 --> 01:30:06,117
SHE'S OUT THERE ALL ALONE,
ISN'T SHE ?

996
01:30:11,724 --> 01:30:13,391
YES.

997
01:30:59,705 --> 01:31:01,706
WHAT HAPPENED ?

998
01:31:01,774 --> 01:31:04,009
I HAVE THE
TELEPHONE RECORDS.
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT ?

999
01:31:04,076 --> 01:31:06,644
WHATEVER GOVERNMENT OFFICIAL
CALLED HONG LING THAT NIGHT...

1000
01:31:06,712 --> 01:31:10,382
ALSO HAD CONVERSATIONS
WITH A P.S.B. OFFICER
NAMED HUAN MINGLU.

1001
01:31:10,449 --> 01:31:12,884
IT DOESN'T MATTER.
I DON'T WANT YOU HURT.

1002
01:31:12,951 --> 01:31:16,854
I HAVE REQUESTED
HIS PRESENCE IN COURT TODAY.

1003
01:31:16,923 --> 01:31:20,725
IT DOES MATTER.
IT WILL MATTER.

1004
01:31:24,696 --> 01:31:26,798
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS ?

1005
01:31:26,865 --> 01:31:29,434
YOU COULD BE TAKEN...

1006
01:31:29,501 --> 01:31:33,104
FROM YOUR HOUSE,
FROM YOUR GRANDMOTHER.

1007
01:31:33,172 --> 01:31:37,442
YOU COULD BE SENT AWAY
OR PUT HERE... OR WORSE.

1008
01:31:40,313 --> 01:31:42,513
SO WHY ARE YOU DOING IT ?

1009
01:31:46,618 --> 01:31:49,354
I'M DOING THIS
BECAUSE...

1010
01:31:49,422 --> 01:31:52,590
I DO NOT WISH
TO BE SILENT ANYMORE.

1011
01:32:16,782 --> 01:32:19,617
SUPERVISING JUDGES.
THEY ARE HERE TO MONITOR.

1012
01:32:19,685 --> 01:32:22,053
<i>IT MEANS
TODAY IS THE DAY.</i>

1013
01:32:22,121 --> 01:32:24,889
PROCURATOR GENERAL YANG
NEXT TO GENERAL HONG.

1014
01:32:24,957 --> 01:32:27,192
<i>AND MANY OF
THE PARTY ELDERS.</i>

1015
01:32:28,793 --> 01:32:30,727
[Chairman Xu
In Chinese]

1016
01:32:30,794 --> 01:32:35,565
[Female Interpreter]
THIS FINAL SESSION
OF OUR PEOPLE'S COURT...

1017
01:32:35,633 --> 01:32:39,769
HEARING CRIMINAL CASE 4-1-1-6
IS NOW OPEN.

1018
01:32:41,805 --> 01:32:44,507
COURT IS IN SESSION.
ADVOCATE SHEN YUELIN.

1019
01:32:44,575 --> 01:32:48,245
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
I WISH TO SUMMON HUAN MINGLU
TO THE WITNESS STAND.

1020
01:32:48,312 --> 01:32:52,348
[Male Interpreter]
HUAN MINGLU HAS NOT BEEN
INTRODUCED AS A WITNESS.

1021
01:32:52,416 --> 01:32:55,518
THIS MAN MAY KNOW THE TRUTH
OF WHAT HAPPENED TO HONG LING.

1022
01:32:55,586 --> 01:33:00,090
[Female Interpreter]  ADVOCATE
SHEN YUELIN, THIS APPEARS
TO BE A DIVERSIONARY TACTIC.

1023
01:33:00,158 --> 01:33:03,393
[Male Interpreter]
THIS IS PURE MANIPULATION
OF THE FACTS.

1024
01:33:03,460 --> 01:33:06,029
[Chinese]
[Female Interpreter]  ADVOCATE
SHEN YUELIN, REQUEST DENIED.

1025
01:33:06,097 --> 01:33:11,534
I CAN OFFER EVIDENCE
THAT HUAN MINGLU ATTACKED
THE ACCUSED AND ME IN DAZHALAN.

1026
01:33:11,602 --> 01:33:15,738
[Female Interpreter]
SUCH EVIDENCE IS OUTSIDE
THE SCOPE OF THIS PROCEEDING.

1027
01:33:15,806 --> 01:33:20,243
AND ATTEMPTED TO MURDER
THE ACCUSED IN BEIJING
NUMBER ONE DETENTION CENTER.

1028
01:33:20,311 --> 01:33:22,578
[Male Interpreter]
I MUST PROTEST
ONCE MORE AGAIN.

1029
01:33:22,646 --> 01:33:27,383
THIS IS CRUCIAL EVIDENCE
THAT SUGGESTS
THE ACCUSED IS INNOCENT.

1030
01:33:27,451 --> 01:33:29,920
[Chinese]
[Female Interpreter]
ADVOCATE SHEN YUELIN,

1031
01:33:29,987 --> 01:33:32,622
THERE'S A PROCEDURE FOR BRINGING
UNRELATED CHARGES.

1032
01:33:32,690 --> 01:33:34,624
WHEN WILL THAT BE ?

1033
01:33:34,692 --> 01:33:39,729
AFTER MY CLIENT IS SENTENCED
OR AFTER HE IS EXECUTED ?
ANSWER ME, PLEASE.

1034
01:33:39,797 --> 01:33:41,531
[Female Interpreter]
ENOUGH !

1035
01:33:41,598 --> 01:33:45,969
WE MUST CALL AN END TO TESTIMONY
ONLY INDIRECTLY RELATED.

1036
01:33:46,037 --> 01:33:48,305
<i>PRESIDING CHAIRMAN--
[Chinese]</i>

1037
01:33:48,372 --> 01:33:52,608
[Female Interpreter]
WILL YOU PLEASE SIT DOWN ?

1038
01:33:54,678 --> 01:33:57,280
NO, PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

1039
01:33:57,348 --> 01:34:01,201
- [Chairman Xu In Chinese]
- [Female Interpreter]
WHAT DID YOU SAY ?

1040
01:34:01,268 --> 01:34:04,487
A MAN'S LIFE IS AT STAKE.

1041
01:34:04,555 --> 01:34:07,958
NOT AN AMERICAN LIFE,
NOT A CHINESE LIFE.

1042
01:34:08,025 --> 01:34:11,494
<i>A MAN'S LIFE.
IN SUCH CIRCUMSTANCES...</i>

1043
01:34:11,562 --> 01:34:14,998
WHAT I AM ASKING IS NOT
AN UNREASONABLE REQUEST.

1044
01:34:15,066 --> 01:34:18,835
<i>[Chairman Xu
  In Chinese]</i>

1045
01:34:18,902 --> 01:34:22,305
[Female Interpreter]
I WILL DECIDE WHAT IS REASONABLE
AND UNREASONABLE.

1046
01:34:22,373 --> 01:34:26,042
<i>[Chairman Xu In Chinese]
[Female Interpreter]
NOW SIT DOWN.</i>

1047
01:34:28,212 --> 01:34:32,148
<i>- [Chinese]
- [Female Interpreter]
  I SAID, SIT DOWN.</i>

1048
01:34:32,216 --> 01:34:37,287
THE MATTER IS DECIDED.
THE COURT IS NOT INTERESTED IN
THE TESTIMONY OF SUCH WITNESSES.

1049
01:34:37,355 --> 01:34:40,190
<i>[Chinese]</i>

1050
01:34:40,258 --> 01:34:42,993
[Female Interpreter]
- I AM.
- YOU ARE WHAT ?

1051
01:34:43,060 --> 01:34:46,896
I AM INTERESTED IN HEARING.
WHAT ABOUT YOU ?

1052
01:34:48,665 --> 01:34:51,434
[Chinese]
[Female Interpreter]
I HAVE ALREADY RULED.

1053
01:34:57,541 --> 01:34:59,142
[Chinese]
[Male Interpreter]
WHY NOT ?

1054
01:34:59,210 --> 01:35:02,879
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN, THE VOTE
ON THIS MATTER IS TWO TO ONE.

1055
01:35:02,946 --> 01:35:06,549
WITH THE APPROVAL OF THE COURT,
I SUMMON HUAN MINGLU
AS A WITNESS.

1056
01:35:07,518 --> 01:35:09,552
<i>[Man]
HUAN MINGLU ?</i>

1057
01:35:11,588 --> 01:35:14,057
[Whispering]

1058
01:35:17,561 --> 01:35:19,429
[Whispering]

1059
01:35:22,366 --> 01:35:25,068
WHAT'S HAPPENING ?
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

1060
01:35:25,136 --> 01:35:27,270
[Li Cheng]
YUELIN.

1061
01:35:29,640 --> 01:35:31,707
[Whispering]

1062
01:35:33,077 --> 01:35:35,445
YOU CUT THE SOUND.
I'VE LOST THE SOUND AGAIN !

1063
01:35:35,512 --> 01:35:38,415
IT'S OKAY.
THE PROCURATOR GENERAL
WISHES TO SEE ME.

1064
01:35:38,482 --> 01:35:41,684
WHY DO THEY WANT YOU ?
TRUST ME.
EVERYTHING WILL BE OKAY.

1065
01:35:41,752 --> 01:35:44,120
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

1066
01:36:19,023 --> 01:36:22,058
[Chairman Xu In Chinese]
[Female Interpreter]
BE SEATED.

1067
01:36:22,126 --> 01:36:26,129
[Chairman Xu
In Chinese]

1068
01:36:27,831 --> 01:36:31,167
[Female Interpreter]
I DECLARE THE PEOPLE'S BEIJING
INTERMEDIATE COURT...

1069
01:36:31,235 --> 01:36:36,239
HEARING CRIMINAL CASE 4-1-1-6
ONCE AGAIN OPEN.

1070
01:36:38,376 --> 01:36:41,077
DEFENSE ADVOCATE
IS NOT PRESENT.

1071
01:36:41,145 --> 01:36:45,148
[Jack]  NOR IS HER AIDE.
[Female Interpreter]  THEN
THE WITNESS SHOULD STEP DOWN.

1072
01:36:45,216 --> 01:36:48,818
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN--
NO, WAIT A MINUTE.
TING, TING, TING.

1073
01:36:48,886 --> 01:36:53,423
<i>[Chairman Xu]  YES ?
I'M ENTITLED TO QUESTION
THIS WITNESS.</i>

1074
01:36:53,491 --> 01:36:57,660
YOUR RIGHT TO QUESTION
HAS BEEN PREVIOUSLY
ESTABLISHED.

1075
01:36:57,728 --> 01:37:01,231
<i>YOU MAY DO SO,
BRIEFLY, AND TO THE POINT.</i>

1076
01:37:26,290 --> 01:37:28,358
I CANNOT SIGN IT.

1077
01:37:28,426 --> 01:37:33,596
HUAN MINGLU, AT APPROXIMATELY
2:00 A.M. ON THE MORNING
OF THE MURDER...

1078
01:37:33,664 --> 01:37:37,534
RECORDS INDICATE
THAT YOU RECEIVED A CALL
FROM AN UNLISTED CELL PHONE.

1079
01:37:37,601 --> 01:37:39,669
<i>YOU REMEMBER WHO MADE
THAT CALL ?
[Chinese]</i>

1080
01:37:39,736 --> 01:37:41,804
[Male Interpreter]
IRRELEVANT !  THIS IS A WASTE
OF THE COURT'S TIME.

1081
01:37:41,872 --> 01:37:45,041
[Chairman Xu]
YOU MAY PROCEED, ACCUSED MOORE.
PLEASE BE DIRECT...

1082
01:37:45,109 --> 01:37:50,046
BEFORE EVEN YOUR FRIENDS,
THE PEOPLE'S ASSESSORS,
MAY LOSE THEIR PATIENCE.

1083
01:37:50,114 --> 01:37:52,082
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHO CALLED YOU ?

1084
01:37:52,149 --> 01:37:54,284
<i>[Chinese]
[Male Interpreter]
IT WAS THE WRONG NUMBER.</i>

1085
01:37:54,351 --> 01:37:59,255
<i>WRONG NUMBER ?  THEN WHY DID
THE CALL LAST FIVE MINUTES ?
[Minglu In Chinese]</i>

1086
01:37:59,323 --> 01:38:04,094
[Male Interpreter]
MAYBE IT WAS SOMEONE
TALKATIVE LIKE THE ACCUSED.

1087
01:38:04,161 --> 01:38:07,863
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN, WOULD YOU
INSTRUCT THE WITNESS TO WIPE
THE SMIRK OFF HIS FACE ?

1088
01:38:17,408 --> 01:38:19,409
I CANNOT SIGN IT.

1089
01:38:19,477 --> 01:38:22,945
THEN YOU'LL BE DISMISSED
OF YOUR DUTIES AND DISCIPLINED.

1090
01:38:23,013 --> 01:38:27,117
ACCUSED MOORE,
I AM LOSING MY PATIENCE.

1091
01:38:27,184 --> 01:38:29,219
GET TO THE POINT BEFORE
I DISMISS THE WITNESS.

1092
01:38:29,286 --> 01:38:33,623
HAVE YOU EVER SERVED AS A GUARD
FOR ANY GOVERNMENT OFFICIAL ?

1093
01:38:33,690 --> 01:38:36,326
[Chinese]
[Male Interpreter]
YES.

1094
01:38:36,393 --> 01:38:41,063
- HAVE YOU EVER MET
MINISTER LIN SHOU ?
- [Chairman Xu]  IRRELEVANT.

1095
01:39:08,359 --> 01:39:11,127
HAVE YOU EVER MET GENERAL HONG
OR HIS DAUGHTER HONG LING ?

1096
01:39:11,195 --> 01:39:12,962
[Chinese]
[Chairman Xu]
IRRELEVANT.

1097
01:39:13,030 --> 01:39:16,732
I HAVE ALREADY RULED AGAINST
THIS LINE OF QUESTIONING.

1098
01:39:16,800 --> 01:39:19,369
ALL RIGHT.
HUAN MINGLU,

1099
01:39:19,436 --> 01:39:23,673
AS AN OFFICER IN THE P.S.B.,
DID YOU EVER WORK IN A PRISON--

1100
01:39:23,740 --> 01:39:25,575
[Male Interpreter]
BEYOND THE SCOPE
OF THIS HEARING.

1101
01:39:25,643 --> 01:39:28,744
[Chairman Xu]  SUSTAINED.
ARE YOU FINISHED ?
NO, I AM NOT !

1102
01:39:28,812 --> 01:39:32,815
<i>ON THE EVENING OF APRIL 10,
DID NOT YOU AND TWO
ACCOMPLICES ROUGH ME UP...</i>

1103
01:39:32,883 --> 01:39:35,017
IN DETENTION CENTER
NUMBER ONE ?

1104
01:39:35,085 --> 01:39:36,852
[Male Interpreter]
BEYOND THE SCOPE
OF THIS HEARING.

1105
01:39:36,920 --> 01:39:39,021
SUSTAINED.
ON APRIL 11,

1106
01:39:39,089 --> 01:39:43,826
WHILE I WAS SITTING IN A
P.S.B. CAR IN DAZHALAN, DID YOU
NOT ATTACK ME AND MY ATTORNEY ?

1107
01:39:43,894 --> 01:39:46,262
[Male Interpreter]
- NO.
- IRRELEVANT.

1108
01:39:46,330 --> 01:39:48,698
I HAVE NOT FINISHED
THIS LINE OF QUESTIONING.

1109
01:39:48,765 --> 01:39:51,367
- I HAVE LOST MY PATIENCE.
- WHY--

1110
01:39:51,435 --> 01:39:55,505
WHY WILL YOU NOT
LET THIS WITNESS
ANSWER MY QUESTIONS ?

1111
01:39:55,573 --> 01:39:57,740
HE JUST SITS THERE,
LAUGHING AT ME !

1112
01:39:57,808 --> 01:40:01,477
<i>LAUGHING AND LYING !</i>

1113
01:40:01,545 --> 01:40:05,848
WHERE'S MY ATTORNEY ?
CAUSING TOO MUCH TROUBLE ?
THAT WHY YOU DRAGGED HER OUT ?

1114
01:40:05,916 --> 01:40:08,451
- YOU ARE IN CONTEMPT.
- IF THAT'S THE CASE--

1115
01:40:08,519 --> 01:40:13,590
WHY DON'T YOU LET HER GO
AND STAY WITH ME ?  YOU'VE
ALREADY MEASURED MY COFFIN !

1116
01:40:13,657 --> 01:40:15,558
I SAID YOU ARE IN CONTEMPT !

1117
01:40:15,626 --> 01:40:19,429
YOU THINK I GIVE A SHIT ?
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO,
SHOOT ME TWICE ?

1118
01:40:19,496 --> 01:40:22,632
LET MY ATTORNEY GO
AND TAKE ME.

1119
01:40:22,700 --> 01:40:27,270
I DON'T HAVE ANY MONEY,
BUT I'VE GOT SOME SHOES.
THEY'LL PAY FOR THE BULLET.

1120
01:40:27,338 --> 01:40:30,072
ALL RIGHT ?  PUT A NICE
DROP CLOTH DOWN.

1121
01:40:30,140 --> 01:40:32,775
YOU CAN PUT A BULLET
RIGHT IN THE BACK OF MY HEAD.
DO IT RIGHT HERE.  BANG !

1122
01:40:32,843 --> 01:40:34,644
BULLET IN THE BACK
OF MY HEAD.

1123
01:40:34,712 --> 01:40:36,713
BAM !  BAM !  BAM !

1124
01:40:36,780 --> 01:40:40,015
DO IT RIGHT HERE RIGHT NOW.
I DON'T WANT TO WAIT.

1125
01:41:39,342 --> 01:41:42,444
<i>[Chairman Xu
  In Chinese]</i>

1126
01:41:42,511 --> 01:41:45,948
[Female Interpreter]
WE WILL NOW PROCEED
TO FINAL ARGUMENTS...

1127
01:41:45,982 --> 01:41:48,283
IF PROCURATOR MA IS PREPARED.

1128
01:41:48,485 --> 01:41:50,986
[Male Interpreter]
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN--

1129
01:42:08,237 --> 01:42:10,338
[Whispering]
FOR YOU.

1130
01:42:13,342 --> 01:42:15,911
[Whispering]
YOUR LAWYER
IS VERY PERSUASIVE.

1131
01:42:39,068 --> 01:42:42,804
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN, I WISH
TO CALL AN ADDITIONAL WITNESS.

1132
01:42:42,872 --> 01:42:44,506
[Male Interpreter]
THIS HAS NO PRECEDENT.

1133
01:42:44,573 --> 01:42:47,943
- [Chinese]
- [Female Interpreter]
I HAVE ALREADY RULED.

1134
01:43:00,222 --> 01:43:04,459
[Hoffmann Speaking
In German]

1135
01:43:06,328 --> 01:43:09,213
[Hoffmann]
MULTIBILLION DOLLAR
SATELLITE UNDERTAKING.

1136
01:43:11,067 --> 01:43:13,001
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,

1137
01:43:13,069 --> 01:43:15,437
<i>I APOLOGIZE TO THE COURT.</i>

1138
01:43:15,504 --> 01:43:20,008
I REQUEST THE COURT'S
PERMISSION TO CALL
AN ADDITIONAL WITNESS.

1139
01:43:21,010 --> 01:43:23,344
I HAVE ALREADY RULED.

1140
01:43:23,412 --> 01:43:25,547
[Male Interpreter]
THE FOREIGNER IS MAKING
A MOCKERY OF THE PEOPLE'S COURT.

1141
01:43:25,614 --> 01:43:28,183
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
I IMPLORE YOU !

1142
01:43:28,250 --> 01:43:31,486
I RECOGNIZE
THAT I HAVE TRIED
THE COURT'S PATIENCE.

1143
01:43:31,554 --> 01:43:34,289
I PROMISE YOU
IT WILL NOT HAPPEN AGAIN.

1144
01:43:35,658 --> 01:43:39,227
THIS WITNESS
IS IN A POSITION TO HAVE
UNIQUE KNOWLEDGE...

1145
01:43:39,295 --> 01:43:41,997
OF THE PROCEEDINGS
OF THIS CASE.

1146
01:43:43,800 --> 01:43:49,237
NOT TO CALL HIM WOULD CALL
INTO QUESTION THE PROCEEDINGS
OF THIS CASE ALTOGETHER.

1147
01:43:49,305 --> 01:43:51,073
PLEASE !

1148
01:43:51,140 --> 01:43:53,809
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
PLEASE, JUST ONE MORE WITNESS.

1149
01:43:53,876 --> 01:43:56,578
- REQUEST DENIED.
- PRESIDING CHAIRMAN.

1150
01:43:56,645 --> 01:44:01,249
THE PROCURATOR GENERAL
HAS GIVEN HIS PERMISSION
TO CALL ANOTHER WITNESS.

1151
01:44:04,386 --> 01:44:07,388
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
I WOULD LIKE TO CALL
MINISTER--

1152
01:44:15,031 --> 01:44:19,735
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN,
I WOULD LIKE
TO CALL LIN DAN.

1153
01:44:19,802 --> 01:44:22,537
[Male Interpreter]
THERE IS NO FOUNDATION
FOR THIS WITNESS.

1154
01:44:26,009 --> 01:44:30,078
[Female Interpreter]
LIN DAN, PLEASE TAKE
THE WITNESS STAND.

1155
01:44:50,867 --> 01:44:52,801
[Chinese]

1156
01:44:52,869 --> 01:44:55,470
[Male Interpreter]
YOU MADE USE OF
THE CRIMINAL CODE I GAVE YOU.

1157
01:44:55,538 --> 01:44:58,706
SPEAK ENGLISH.
I KNOW YOU CAN.

1158
01:45:00,777 --> 01:45:03,078
CONGRATULATIONS
ON YOUR RECENT APPOINTMENT,

1159
01:45:03,146 --> 01:45:05,480
THE PRINCIPAL CHINESE
PROGRAMMING PARTNER...

1160
01:45:05,548 --> 01:45:08,483
FOR HOFFCO TELEKOMM'S
JOINT VENTURE
WITH THE CHINESE GOVERNMENT.

1161
01:45:08,551 --> 01:45:10,618
THANK YOU.

1162
01:45:10,687 --> 01:45:13,321
WONDERFUL OPPORTUNITY.
YES.

1163
01:45:13,389 --> 01:45:18,760
WOULD IT BE ACCURATE TO SAY
THAT MY OWN COMPANY,
McANDREWS COMMUNICATIONS,

1164
01:45:18,828 --> 01:45:21,262
WAS HOFFCO TELEKOMM'S
PRINCIPAL COMPETITOR...

1165
01:45:21,330 --> 01:45:23,799
FOR THAT RECENTLY AWARDED
CONTRACT ?
I SUPPOSE SO.

1166
01:45:23,866 --> 01:45:26,301
YOU SUPPOSE SO.  OKAY.
WOULD IT ALSO BE ACCURATE
TO SAY...

1167
01:45:26,368 --> 01:45:31,840
THAT YOU HAD NO GUARANTEE
OF AN EQUIVALENT PAYOFF
FROM McANDREWS ?

1168
01:45:31,908 --> 01:45:36,344
[Male Interpreter]
PRESIDING CHAIRMAN, "PAYOFF"
HAS NEGATIVE CONNOTATION.

1169
01:45:36,412 --> 01:45:38,613
LET ME REPHRASE.
LIN DAN,

1170
01:45:38,681 --> 01:45:41,783
McANDREWS COMMUNICATIONS
DID NOT OFFER YOU
AN EQUIVALENT POSITION.

1171
01:45:41,851 --> 01:45:46,521
THAT HAD NOT BEEN DISCUSSED.
THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH HONG LING'S MURDER.

1172
01:45:46,589 --> 01:45:48,990
IT HAS EVERYTHING TO DO
WITH HONG LING'S MURDER.

1173
01:45:49,058 --> 01:45:51,359
WOULD YOU SAY MY INDICTMENT...

1174
01:45:51,427 --> 01:45:53,795
WAS RESPONSIBLE
FOR McANDREWS COMMUNICATIONS
LOSING THAT DEAL ?

1175
01:45:53,863 --> 01:45:55,797
[Chinese]
[Male Interpreter]
WHY DOES THE COURT PERMIT THIS ?

1176
01:45:55,865 --> 01:45:59,334
YOU USED HER, DIDN'T YOU ?
YOU USED HER
AND YOU SACRIFICED HER--

1177
01:45:59,401 --> 01:46:02,237
TO SABOTAGE THE DEAL
YOUR FATHER WAS COMPLETING
WITH McANDREWS.

1178
01:46:02,304 --> 01:46:05,040
WITH WHOM HE HAD A LONG
PERSONAL RELATIONSHIP.  IT
COULD'VE LEFT YOU IN THE COLD.

1179
01:46:05,108 --> 01:46:07,142
THESE ARE NOT QUESTIONS.

1180
01:46:07,210 --> 01:46:11,412
BUT THIS IS.
WHAT WAS THE NATURE OF YOUR
RELATIONSHIP WITH HONG LING ?

1181
01:46:11,480 --> 01:46:13,749
I HAD NO RELATIONSHIP
WITH HONG LING.

1182
01:46:13,816 --> 01:46:16,985
NONE AT ALL ?

1183
01:46:17,053 --> 01:46:19,054
WOULD YOU LIKE TO RECONSIDER
THAT STATEMENT ?

1184
01:46:19,122 --> 01:46:23,424
I KNEW HER, KNEW OF HER FAMILY.
BUT THERE WAS NO RELATIONSHIP.

1185
01:46:23,492 --> 01:46:26,728
NO RELATIONSHIP.
HOW DO YOU EXPLAIN THIS ?

1186
01:46:29,665 --> 01:46:32,033
THIS IS HONG LING'S LOCKET.

1187
01:46:32,101 --> 01:46:35,670
SHE WORE IT
THE NIGHT OF THE MURDER.
JUST TURNED UP.

1188
01:46:40,342 --> 01:46:44,112
INSIDE IS A PICTURE
OF GENERAL HONG.

1189
01:46:46,415 --> 01:46:48,784
INSIDE OF THAT,

1190
01:46:48,851 --> 01:46:51,552
IS A CHARMING PHOTOGRAPH...

1191
01:46:51,620 --> 01:46:53,421
OF HONG LING...

1192
01:46:53,489 --> 01:46:55,323
AND...

1193
01:46:55,391 --> 01:46:57,192
YOU.

1194
01:46:57,260 --> 01:47:00,095
[Chairman Xu]
ACCUSED MOORE,
LET ME SEE THIS EVIDENCE.

1195
01:47:04,934 --> 01:47:07,635
[Jack]
PLEASE SHARE THAT WITH
THE PEOPLE'S ASSESSORS.

1196
01:47:07,703 --> 01:47:10,405
THEY SEEM
A LITTLE MORE INTERESTED NOW.

1197
01:47:10,472 --> 01:47:12,573
ALSO, PROCURATOR MA,

1198
01:47:12,641 --> 01:47:14,876
<i>YOU'RE NOT SMILING
SO MUCH.</i>

1199
01:47:17,013 --> 01:47:20,315
WHY WOULD THERE BE
A PHOTOGRAPH OF YOU AND
HONG LING INSIDE HER LOCKET ?

1200
01:47:20,382 --> 01:47:22,818
THERE WAS NO RELATIONSHIP.

1201
01:47:22,885 --> 01:47:25,153
I KNEW HER THE WAY
MANY MEN KNEW HER.

1202
01:47:25,221 --> 01:47:28,589
<i>THE WAY YOU KNEW HER.
[Yuelin]
BUT YOU DID KNOW HER ?</i>

1203
01:47:28,657 --> 01:47:31,059
<i>ANSWER ME.
[Li Dan]
I KNEW HER A LONG TIME AGO.</i>

1204
01:47:31,127 --> 01:47:34,229
I HAD NOT TALKED TO--

1205
01:47:34,297 --> 01:47:38,834
I HAD NOT TALKED TO HER
SINCE I CAN'T REMEMBER WHEN.
[Jack]  CAN'T REMEMBER WHEN ?

1206
01:47:38,901 --> 01:47:40,836
ADVOCATE SHEN YUELIN,
WILL YOU ENTER
THE PHONE RECORDS...

1207
01:47:40,903 --> 01:47:44,139
INTO EVIDENCE, PLEASE ?
ON THE NIGHT HONG LING
WAS KILLED,

1208
01:47:44,207 --> 01:47:46,641
THREE CALLS WERE MADE
FROM THIS NUMBER.

1209
01:47:46,709 --> 01:47:49,144
- TWO CALLS WERE RECEIVED.
- [Male Interpreter]
OBJECTION !

1210
01:47:49,212 --> 01:47:52,613
THE FIRST CALL RECEIVED
WAS FROM HONG LING
EARLY THAT NIGHT.

1211
01:47:52,681 --> 01:47:54,615
THEN LATER,
AROUND 2:00 A.M.,

1212
01:47:54,683 --> 01:47:59,087
<i>A CALL WAS MADE
FOR A NUMBER REGISTERED
TO HUAN MINGLU.</i>

1213
01:47:59,155 --> 01:48:03,358
AT 3:10 A.M., THE SECOND
CALL MADE WAS TO A NUMBER
REGISTERED TO HONG LING.

1214
01:48:03,425 --> 01:48:05,493
[Male Interpreter]
WHAT DO THESE
TELEPHONE NUMBERS--

1215
01:48:05,561 --> 01:48:10,631
<i>AT 5:41 A.M., A CALL
WAS APPARENTLY RECEIVED
FROM HUAN MINGLU.</i>

1216
01:48:10,699 --> 01:48:12,767
AT 5:46 A.M.,

1217
01:48:12,835 --> 01:48:16,637
A TWO-MINUTE CALL
WAS MADE FROM THIS NUMBER
TO POLICE HEADQUARTERS.

1218
01:48:16,705 --> 01:48:20,375
[Interpreters]
- THIS IS CHAOS
- I WILL HAVE YOU REMOVED.

1219
01:48:20,442 --> 01:48:23,478
- LIN DAN, DO YOU OWN
A CELLULAR TELEPHONE ?
- YES OR NO ?

1220
01:48:23,545 --> 01:48:25,646
I DO.

1221
01:48:25,714 --> 01:48:27,949
CAN YOU GIVE THE COURT
THE NUMBER OF THAT PHONE ?

1222
01:48:28,017 --> 01:48:31,719
I AM NOT A SECRETARY,
AND I RARELY CALL MYSELF,
SO I WOULD NEED TO CHECK IT.

1223
01:48:31,787 --> 01:48:35,690
IS THE NUMBER OF YOUR
CELL PHONE 5-1-7-8-5-7 ?

1224
01:48:35,758 --> 01:48:37,325
NO, IT IS NOT.

1225
01:48:37,393 --> 01:48:40,528
YOU'RE QUITE SURE ?
EVEN THOUGH YOU RARELY
CALL YOURSELF ?

1226
01:48:40,596 --> 01:48:42,764
YES, I AM QUITE SURE.

1227
01:48:44,200 --> 01:48:48,803
[Jack]  WHO DO YOU THINK
HAS THAT NUMBER ?
5-1-7-8-5-7.

1228
01:48:53,542 --> 01:48:58,045
IS THE TELEPHONE NUMBER YOURS,
MINISTER LIN SHOU ?

1229
01:49:05,086 --> 01:49:08,222
IT IS MY NUMBER.

1230
01:49:10,976 --> 01:49:13,861
[Male Interpreter]
DON'T, FATHER.

1231
01:49:13,928 --> 01:49:18,199
DON'T WHAT ?
I'M NOT AFRAID.

1232
01:49:18,267 --> 01:49:20,034
WHY ARE YOU AFRAID ?

1233
01:49:20,101 --> 01:49:23,804
YOU USED YOUR FATHER'S PHONE
'CAUSE YOU KNEW THE RECORDS
OF AN OFFICIAL CAN BE WITHHELD.

1234
01:49:23,872 --> 01:49:26,740
HONG LING WAS SUPPOSED
TO SET ME UP IN SOME WAY,
WASN'T SHE ?

1235
01:49:28,243 --> 01:49:31,379
WHATEVER IT WAS,
SHE CHANGED HER MIND.

1236
01:49:31,446 --> 01:49:34,549
THEN SOMEONE GOT IN,
DRUGGED ME WITH CHLOROFORM.

1237
01:49:35,383 --> 01:49:38,018
ISN'T THAT WHAT HAPPENED ?
WAS IT--

1238
01:49:38,086 --> 01:49:41,355
WAS IT HUAN MINGLU ?

1239
01:49:41,423 --> 01:49:44,124
[Chairman Xu]
SUCH SPECULATION
IS OUT OF ORDER.

1240
01:49:44,192 --> 01:49:48,229
SHE RESISTED !

1241
01:49:48,297 --> 01:49:50,330
AND SHE ENDED UP DEAD !

1242
01:49:53,968 --> 01:49:58,288
HE KILLED HER, DIDN'T HE ?
SHE GOT KILLED
AND I GOT SET UP !

1243
01:50:00,809 --> 01:50:02,910
I WASN'T THERE.
ASK HIM.

1244
01:50:02,977 --> 01:50:04,812
<i>DA GUAR.</i>

1245
01:50:05,897 --> 01:50:08,482
WHAT DID HE JUST SAY ?
WHAT DID HE JUST SAY ?

1246
01:50:08,550 --> 01:50:13,521
<i>WHAT ?  DA GUAR ?  THAT'S WHAT
HONG LING SAID THAT NIGHT.
SHE SAID IT OVER AND OVER.</i>

1247
01:50:13,589 --> 01:50:18,259
<i>- DA GUAR.
- DA GUAR, DA GUAR.
  WO MEN DE--</i>

1248
01:50:18,327 --> 01:50:20,027
